{"tid":1879450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話搞工會，但一笑人唔罷工就問我點解自己唔罷工，跟邊邊先啱啊？","createTime":"2020-02-14T08:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T17:49:41.000Z","uid":16846,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12abf96ef5ced7cb9e1d4469fbccc46af1795708","tid":1879450,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"成日話尊重醫護決定復工(送死)，又係咁反問笑佢哋復工嘅人又有冇罷工<br />\n咁點解就算有咗工會，都唔係由各界工會一齊發動罷工嘅？<br />\n明明其他工會可以喺醫護罷工嗰陣撐起佢哋<br />\n或者而家有另一個工會發動罷工，俾醫護加入返<br />\n點解啲工會好似冇曬動靜，要好似以前咁逐隻逐隻喺連登問「咁你罷咗工未啊」咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係又係cap埋轉尾水就走？"},{"pid":"2ba7e41460aa915edc9ee01b9cd44a6d55cab12c","tid":1879450,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964d7b0f321d48f50cc688080965a4ea9aad7397","tid":1879450,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be1f0e3558a7fa274d4028aeb68585c626caddd","tid":1879450,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"班問人有冇罷工撚去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}